# llz local credential cache — NEVER commit. Holds the Linode PAT, GitHub PATs,
# and the OBJ state key `llz tokens` gathers (mode 0600). `llz` reads it locally
# and pushes the secrets to the infra-<env> GitHub Environment; the files stay here.
.llz/

# Terraform working dirs + state. State lives in the remote OBJ backend, never in
# git; the plugin cache + plans are local build artifacts.
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log

# AI coding assistants — per-developer LOCAL state only (can carry local env vars,
# tool permissions, and machine paths). The SHARED config is meant to be COMMITTED,
# so this deliberately does NOT ignore it: CLAUDE.md, .claude/settings.json +
# .claude/commands/ + .claude/agents/, and .github/copilot-instructions.md.
.claude/settings.local.json
.aider*

# Editor / IDE local state. The Dev Container (.devcontainer/) carries the shared
# editor setup via customizations.vscode, so a repo-level .vscode/.idea is
# per-developer. (.devcontainer/ itself IS committed — it's the toolchain.)
.vscode/
.idea/

# OS cruft
.DS_Store
*.swp
